🚆 Travel Booking System (DBMS Project)

📌 Description

This project is a Travel Booking System developed using MySQL. It manages customer bookings, travel schedules, and payments efficiently.

---

📊 Features

- Customer Registration
- Travel Search
- Ticket Booking
- Payment Management
- Seat Availability Tracking
- Automatic Seat Update (Triggers)

---

🗂️ Database Tables

- Customers
- Travel
- Booking
- Payment

---

⚙️ Technologies Used

- MySQL (SQL)
- DBMS Concepts

